<br />\n結果要去私家檢查先話要做手術<br />\n<br />\n我想去私家快手攪掂佢<br />\n但我又唔知幾錢同邊間檢查好<br />\n<br />\n求巴打/身邊人如果曾經經歷過可唔可以俾啲建議我<br />\n應該去邊間檢查好<br />\n應該係秘尿科定腫癌科<br />\n同埋可唔可以請埋幾錢，我窮撚想預吓budget <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:12:16.000Z","msg":"有機會係靜脈曲張<br />\n利申: 試過, 一開始好撚驚, 後尾照超聲波冇事"},{"pid":"f6f9d44de4fb2ed184647fd16f3807d981b14e3a","tid":868730,"uid":68,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de6c98d2a0100e65e5e01a041aa3692d13fb235f","tid":868730,"uid":31252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"私家醫院秘尿科 手術5,6皮一定走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n利申：窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  手術 化療 全部喺公立做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"我手術係私家做 四皮半<br />\n化療係公立做 每次$145<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb3f200fc98a5187b951f4e8efa8c6c4d32241f","tid":868730,"uid":96246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"靜脈曲張姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好多男人都有"},{"pid":"42944a4dea395042c6bf3d3f3e67336c594a9871","tid":868730,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:03:14.000Z","msg":"屌睾丸有事就即刻去急症啦<br />\n拖拖下以後都冇得生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}